data.description: Discover the epitome of Florida living in this Key West-style gem, a pool home nestled along a tranquil canal with NO HOA. Bask in the beauty of your outdoor oasis with a recently built salt water pool with enclosure. Featuring an ample sun-shelf, bubblers, umbrella holder, waterfall spouts, LED lighting and Thermeau heating system. Inside and you'll love the high vaulted ceilings and split bedroom floor plan. Walk over to the kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and quality soft close cabinets. Relish the charm indoors with plantation shutters and practicality  with accordion shutters, providing both elegance and hurricane protection. Conveniently located near shopping and pristine beaches, this home offer perfect blend of comfort, style, and coastal convenience. Your dream Florida lifestyle awaits.
